  "merger_description": "Danaher Corporation (**Danaher**) proposes to acquire 100% of the outstanding share capital of Masimo Corporation (**Masimo**).\n\nDanaher is a global science and technology company. Danaher designs, manufactures and markets professional, medical, industrial and commercial products and services under three core segments: biotechnology, life sciences, and diagnostics.\n\nMasimo is a global medical technology company. Masimo is a provider of pulse oximetry and other patient sensors and monitoring solutions.",
